data.description: Beautiful 2 story home on finished basement in sought after Sky Country! The main floor features a beautiful kitchen with granite counters, breakfast area and attached dining room large enough to accommodate a 10 person table, an inviting family room with gas fireplace, an office, half bath, laundry room and access to the huge deck that is perfect for entertaining. Upstairs is an oversized owner's suite with private bath, 2 additional bedrooms and another full bath. The basement (accessible from inside the home or from the private garage) has been fully redone with new carpet/flooring, new doors, new drywall/paint. It features a bedroom, bonus room, living room w/gas fireplace and a private covered patio. Lumpkin County is home to many attractions (historic downtown, shops, outdoor activities) as well as the University of North Georgia. Air B&B/rent the basement or whole home if you desire. The Property Owner's Association is voluntary.
